claim: The US Open is a continuation of Wimbledon.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Other notable names who were successful on the tour were Zina Garrison  (  World No. 4 and 1990 Wimbledon finalist  )  , Natasha Zvereva  (  World No. 1 in doubles  )  , Magdalena Maleeva  (  World No. 4  )  , Cara Black  (  World No. 1 and 10-time Grand Slam champion in doubles and mixed doubles  )  , Nadia Petrova  (  World No. 3 and two-time Grand Slam semifinalist  )  , Agnieszka Radwanska  (  World No. 2 and 2012 Wimbledon finalist  )  , Karolina Pliskova  (  2016 US Open finalist  )  , Eugenie Bouchard  (  2014 Wimbledon finalist  )  and Belinda Bencic  (  World No. 7 and 2014 US Open quarterfinalist  )  .
